Follow guide to Download and Install Eform-Angular-Frontend project on [Page Installation](https://sites.google.com/s/1R1FZotyoOPczaFaZs13O9XLailEqG6Zy/p/10d-1PjBIFDkMCouo_lsIvyLHE-SCkdaK/edit)

### Step 2:

```text
cd ~/Documents/workspace/microting

git clone https://github.com/microting/eform-angular-machinearea-plugin.git
```

### Step 3:

```text
cp -av eform-angular-machinearea-plugin/eform-client/src/app/plugins/modules/machine-area-pn eform-angular-frontend/eform-client/src/app/plugins/modules/
```

### Step 4:

```text
mkdir -p ~/Documents/workspace/microting/eform-angular-frontend/eFormAPI/Plugins
```
